{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>&quot;Sodaman is infuriated, ever since Entity-X caused the Sodacalypse, making almost all of the sodas in the existence go flat, becoming bland and tasteless with the press of a button. Yet there are still some out there, untouched by this catastrophe and it is up to Sodaman himself to find them.&quot;</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>&quot;I'm here to drink soda and kick aliens... but I'm all outta soda.&quot;</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178990/extras/actionGIF.gif?t=1738515060\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u00a0 \u00a0 Chug Sodas Down</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Choose from a variety of soda powers across 7 different colors, mix, shake, add a little dash of fury and create the freshest builds found in this side of the universe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178990/extras/SodaSCrollGIF.gif?t=1738515060\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Arm Yourself</h2></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Choose the weapon most suited to your playstyle and discover the most powerful synergies. <br> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178990/extras/armoryGIF.gif?t=1738515060\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Augment Yourself</h2></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> With six different body parts and over 30 cybernetic augments available for implementation, you'll have endless options for character customization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178990/extras/augmentGIF.gif?t=1738515060\" /></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u00a0 \u00a0 Build Your Deck</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from dozens of power-up cards and build your deck. Take your soda power to the next level!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178990/extras/cardGIF.gif?t=1738515060\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u00a0 \u00a0 Explore Your Spaceship</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Relax between runs in your spaceship, meet new characters and explore more of the Sodaman universe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178990/extras/spaceshipGIF.gif?t=1738515060\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178990/extras/NPCS-ezgif.com-resize.gif?t=1738515060\" /> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;We\u2019re a small team of 4 devs creating the game. So if you have any question, suggestions or just want to hang out, grab a six-pack and join our Discord.&quot;</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178990/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738515060","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178990/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738515060","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178990/649f4d06a40a18873c1127ffcf5293c278866761/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738515060","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178990/649f4d06a40a18873c1127ffcf5293c278866761/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738515060","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes"